    "author": "1356970554027933877",
    "text": "⚠️Ship: Goliath×Caecus⚠️\nEven our eyes meeting, down to the softest breath,\nthe love leaking through,\nlike a gentle breeze among the clouds,\nwill find its way to you, completely unchanged.\n​—— P1Harmo",
    "orig_filename": "Image_1779208594037.png",
    "refreshed": true,
    "file": "discord_1506355833162830005.png",
    "status": "ok"
  },
  {
    "source": "discord",
    "channel": "🔸art-and-memes",
    "author": "1356970554027933877",
    "text": "There are violets in your eyes\nThere are guns that blaze around you\nThere are roses in between my thighs and fire that surrounds you\nIt's no wonder every man in town had neither fought nor found you\nE",
    "orig_filename": "Image_1779207691377.png",
    "refreshed": true,
    "file": "discord_1506341542602866793.png",
    "status": "ok"
  },
